data.description: Enjoy easy cottage-style living on LBI in this classic mid-island gem.  This property has a long and lovely LBI history and it’s just waiting for your personal touches to make it your own and start a new generation of memories in Surf City.  The house was minimally damaged During Superstorm Sandy and raised thereafter; electric was upgraded, and a tankless water heater added at that time.  This house has retained its old-island charm through the years and offers three bedrooms, 1.5 baths, a classic outdoor shower and ample parking under the house.  The property features an eat-in kitchen adjacent to the back deck as well as a dining room off the opposite side of the kitchen.  This full-size parcel is 50’x100’ and an easy walk to the beach, the bay or downtown Surf City.  Make this your own today!
